Subject: [PATCH] deps/GLFW: Disable OSMesa support

It's disabled in the Freedesktop SDK:
https://gitlab.com/freedesktop-sdk/freedesktop-sdk/-/issues/1215#note_580204705
---
 deps/GLFW/GLFW.cmake | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/deps/GLFW/GLFW.cmake b/deps/GLFW/GLFW.cmake
index d6a7384d1fdc..f902406ed63e 100644
--- a/deps/GLFW/GLFW.cmake
+++ b/deps/GLFW/GLFW.cmake
@@ -21,6 +21,7 @@ bambustudio_add_cmake_project(GLFW
         -DGLFW_BUILD_DOCS=OFF
         -DGLFW_BUILD_EXAMPLES=OFF
 	-DGLFW_BUILD_TESTS=OFF
+	-DGLFW_USE_OSMESA=OFF
 	${_glfw_use_wayland}
 )
 
